title: MS-DOS 6 PACK
description:
Legacy software for you to play with...




MS-DOS 6 PACK:

Contains MS-DOS 6.21 and 6.22 plus drivers for mouse and CD drive.

All are .ima files

I don't see any keys and I'm not sure if they even used them then. Maybe you just beat two rocks together or something. (He said as if he hadn't come up in the '70s, LOL)


I got this off the old Demonoid because I'm a pack rat. Cleaning out my drives so I'm uploading it here for Posterity.

After that it gets burned to a DVD with a bunch of other old stuff and stuck in an old, dark warehouse forever.
